</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-25_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-26_ pf-text-1">According to the Health and Safety Executive (HSE), thousands of injuries occur in educational settings in the UK each year, many of which could benefit from immediate first aid response.











