</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-iqVWFU kwUChp pf-45_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-46_ pf-text-1"><strong>Health and Safety (First-aid) Regulations 1981</strong> - These regulations require all educational establishments to have adequate first aid equipment, facilities, and personnel tailored to each institution's circumstances.












